<p>John and Dave start by helping answer your questions about iOS 8 Cookies, Bubbbles, Newsttand and Stocks. Then it&#39;s on to answering your questions about using your Mac to translate audio into text, migrating your Mac to a new drive and handling Apple&#39;s Customer Relations department. All this and more in this weeks episode. Download today and enjoy!</p>
